OL,5, Parents are still being forced to spend
OL,6, hundreds of pounds on school uniform   
OL,7, despite rules meant to lower the costs.
OL,9,FThe Children's Society found parents   
OL,10,Fspent on average #422 a year on        
OL,11,Fsecondary and #287 on primary uniforms.
OL,13,FSome school rules that required parents
OL,14,Fto buy costlier branded items were     
OL,15,Fpartly to blame, it said. One mum told 
OL,16,Fthe BBC constantly replacing damaged   
OL,17,Fclothing made it even more expensive.  
OL,19,FThe government says it is working to   
OL,20,Fensure "uniform costs are reasonable". 
